article.headline: Clay scores 20 as Missouri State downs Sam Houston 69-60
article.description: — Donovan Clay scored 20 points as Missouri State beat Sam Houston 69-60 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Clay scores 20 as Missouri State downs Sam Houston 69-60
article.story: SPRINGFIELD, Mo. -- — Donovan Clay scored 20 points as Missouri State beat Sam Houston 69-60 on Saturday night. Clay also had six rebounds for the Bears (7-3). Alston Mason added 18 points and Damien Mayo Jr. finished with 13 points. Davon Barnes finished with 16 points for the Bearkats (5-5). Kian Scroggins added 10 points and 10 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
